text: Best home-based board game cafe with a beautiful view! Ran by a lovely couple. Super chill vibes. Great design sense too. 10/10 would come back for the matcha latte.

Our hosts were this beautiful young couple! My favourite was the matcha which the lady boss also allowed me to have a hand in whisking it myself just for fun. Toilet was very clean, even has a bidet üôèüèª

A surprising hidden gem that we stumbled upon by accident. The Bee Knees was perfect and tasty. Matcha drinks were also on point. There were even board games we could play for free. 10/10 would come by again
owner is super friendly and even offered complimentary drinks and goodies
